file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: DNVGL RP-O501 REST Api
  description: EROSIVE WEAR IN PIPING SYSTEMS
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: https://api.veracity.com/ext/dnvgl/rpo501
paths:
  /v2015/api/componentranking/blackoilstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ComponentRanking
      summary: "Calculates relative erosion and relative criticality for a set of components (Line object) and a single\r\nflow condition specified through a BlackOilStream object and a ParticleStream object."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBlackOilStream\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how the various components are defined."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-componentranking-blackoilstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBlackOilStream
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBlackOilStream'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentRanking'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/componentranking/basicstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ComponentRanking
      summary: "Calculates relative erosion and relative criticality for a set of components (Line object) and a single\r\nflow condition specified through a BasicStream object and a ParticleStream object."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBasicStream\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how the various components are defined."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-componentranking-basicstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBasicStream
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBasicStream'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentRanking'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/erosion/single/blackoilstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ErosionSingle
      summary: "Calculates erosion in mm/ton sand and mm/year for a set of components (Line object) and a single flow\r\ncondition. Mixture velocity is also returned."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBlackOilStream\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how to specify input."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-erosion-single-blackoilstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBlackOilStream
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBlackOilStream'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentResult'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/erosion/single/basicstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ErosionSingle
      summary: "Calculates erosion in mm/ton sand and mm/year for a set of components (Line object) and a single flow\r\ncondition. Mixture velocity is also returned."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBasicStream\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how to specify input."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-erosion-single-basicstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBasicStream
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBasicStream'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentResult'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/erosion/timeseries/blackoilstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ErosionTimeSeries
      summary: "Calculates erosion in mm/ton sand and mm/year for a set of components (Line object) and a time series of flow\r\nconditions."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBlackOilStreamTimeSeries\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how the various components are defined."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-erosion-timeseries-blackoilstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBlackOilStreamTimeSeries
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBlackOilStreamTimeSeries'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiErosionTimeseriesBlackoilstreamPost200ApplicationJsonResponse'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/erosion/timeseries/basicstream:
    post:
      tags:
        - ErosionTimeSeries
      summary: "Calculates erosion in mm/ton sand and mm/year for a set of components (Line object) and a single flow\r\ncondition. Mixture velocity is also returned."
      description: "REQUEST SCHEMA: LineBasicStreamTimeSeries\r\n\r\nConsult the examples and sub-schemas for details on how the various components are defined."
      operationId: post-v2015-api-erosion-timeseries-basicstream
      requestBody:
        description: LineBasicStreamTimeSeries
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LineBasicStreamTimeSeries'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiErosionTimeseriesBasicstreamPost200ApplicationJsonResponse'
        '400':
          description: Invalid or insufficient input. This includes valid input that is outside the model ranges.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/PredefinedErosiveAgent:
    get:
      tags:
        - PredefinedErosiveAgent
      summary: "Provides access to default (RP-O501) density and reduction factor for the erosive agents Quartz, Barite and\r\nCalcite."
      description: 'Schema: None'
      operationId: get-v2015-api-predefinederosiveagent
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedErosiveAgentGet200TextPlainResponse'
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedErosiveAgentGet200ApplicationJsonResponse'
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedErosiveAgentGet200TextJsonResponse'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  '/v2015/api/PredefinedErosiveAgent/{erosiveAgentName}':
    get:
      tags:
        - PredefinedErosiveAgent
      summary: "Provides access to default (RP-O501) density and reduction factor for a specific predefined erosive agent\r\nas specified by name 'erosiveAgentName'."
      description: 'Schema: None.'
      operationId: get-v2015-api-predefinederosiveagent-erosiveagentname
      parameters:
        - name: erosiveAgentName
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErosiveAgent'
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErosiveAgent'
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErosiveAgent'
        '400':
          description: Invalid erosive agent name.
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  /v2015/api/PredefinedTargetMaterial:
    get:
      tags:
        - PredefinedTargetMaterial
      summary: Provides access to default (RP-O501) coefficients K / n and density for all predefined target materials.
      description: 'Schema: None'
      operationId: get-v2015-api-predefinedtargetmaterial
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedTargetMaterialGet200TextPlainResponse'
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedTargetMaterialGet200ApplicationJsonResponse'
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/V2015ApiPredefinedTargetMaterialGet200TextJsonResponse'
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
  '/v2015/api/PredefinedTargetMaterial/{targetMaterialName}':
    get:
      tags:
        - PredefinedTargetMaterial
      summary: "Provides access to default (RP-O501) coefficients K / n and density for a specific predefined target\r\nmaterial as specified by name 'TargetMaterialName'."
      description: 'Schema: None.'
      operationId: get-v2015-api-predefinedtargetmaterial-targetmaterialname
      parameters:
        - name: targetMaterialName
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
            text/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        '400':
          description: Invalid target material name.
        '500':
          description: Calculation error. Unhandled exceptions.
components:
  schemas:
    BlackOilStream:
      type: object
      properties:
        temperatureStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Temperature at standard (reference) condition: [deg C]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        pressureStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Pressure at standard (reference) condition: [Bar abs]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        gasMolWeight:
          type: number
          description: 'Mol weight (MW) of gas: [g/mol]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        oilDensityStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Density of oil phase: [kg/m3]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        waterDensityStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Density of water phase: [kg/m3]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        gasViscosity:
          type: number
          description: 'Viscosity of gas phase: [Pas]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        oilViscosity:
          type: number
          description: 'Viscosity of oil phase: [Pas]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        waterViscosity:
          type: number
          description: 'Viscosity of water phase: [Pas]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        gasCompressibilityFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Gas compressibility factor: [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        temperature:
          type: number
          description: 'Temperature: [deg C]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        pressure:
          type: number
          description: 'Pressure: [bar absolute]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        gasVolumetricRateStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Gas rate at standard conditions: [m3/day]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        oilVolumetricRateStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Oil rate at standard conditions: [m3/day]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        waterVolumetricRateStd:
          type: number
          description: 'Water rate at standard conditions: [m3/day]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: "Defines a single 'snapshot' of a fluid stream according to the simplified \"Black oil\" equation of state.\r\n\"Black oil\" assumes no flashing or absorption, meaning the gas fraction will behave as an ideal gas, and that\r\nthe oil and water phases retain their properties (density/viscosity) regardless of pressure or temperature.\r\nFlow rates are given with reference to a standard condition, for which pressure and temperature are known, i.e.\r\na volumetric gas flow rate in Sm3/d assumes that the gas density is equal to that of the reference condition\r\ngiven by PressureStd and TemperatureStd.\r\n            \r\nMixture density and mixture viscosity are calculated based on the volume weighted fractions of gas. oil and\r\nwater, and these are used as inputs to the erosion calculations."
    ErosiveAgent:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          description: 'Name of predefined erosive agent, or custom name (optional).'
          nullable: true
        density:
          type: number
          description: 'Density of erosive agent [kg/m3]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        reductionFactor:
          type: number
          description: "ReductionFactor [-] Correction factor enabling adjustment of the erosive response based on geometric properties\r\nof the erosive agents. For example, proppants would typically be modelled with ReductionFactor > 1.\r\nA value of 1.0 corresponds to standard RP-O501 models."
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: "Describes the erosive agent present in a fluid stream.\r\n\r\nTo use predefined erosive agent properties (see separate endpoint), specify the name of the predefined\r\nerosive agent. In this case, the values of Density and ReductionFactor will be ignored,\r\nand the corresponding predefined erosive agent values will be applied.\r\nIf Name does not correspond to a predefined erosive agent, the values of Density, and ReductionFactor must be\r\nspecified."
    ParticleStream:
      type: object
      properties:
        particleDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Representative particle diameter. Typically set to d50 for the particle size distribution: [microns]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        particleMassFlowRate:
          type: number
          description: 'Particle mass flow rate: [g/s]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosiveAgent:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErosiveAgent'
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Defines the particle content in a fluid stream.
    AngleDependencyOption:
      enum:
        - Ductile
        - DuctileLegacy
        - Brittle
      type: string
    TargetMaterial:
      type: object
      properties:
        angleDependency:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/AngleDependencyOption'
        name:
          type: string
          description: 'Name of predefined target material, or custom name (optional).'
          nullable: true
        density:
          type: number
          description: 'Density of target material [kg/m3]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        k:
          type: number
          description: Constant of proportionality in RP-O501 response equation
          format: double
          nullable: true
        n:
          type: number
          description: Velocity exponent in RP-O501 response equation
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: "To use predefined target material properties (see separate endpoint), specify the name of the predefined\r\ntarget material. In this case, the values of AngleDependencyOption, Density, K and N will be ignored,\r\nand the corresponding predefined material values will be applied.\r\nIf Name does not correspond to a predefined target material, the values of AngleDependencyOption Density,\r\nK and N must be specified."
    Bend:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        radiusOfCurvature:
          type: number
          description: 'Radius of curvature for the pipe, expressed in number of inner diameters [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Bend geometry model definition.
    Tee:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe at inlet/outlet [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Blinded tee geometry model definition.
    Reducer:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        inletDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Inlet diameter of contraction [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        outletDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Outlet diameter of contraction [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        projectedAngleInDegrees:
          type: number
          description: 'Angle between the pipe axis and the surface of the contracting part of the pipe [deg]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Reducer/contraction geometry model definition.
    ErProbe:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        projectedAngleInDegrees:
          type: number
          description: 'Angle between the pipe axis and surface of the probe elements [deg]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Erosion probe (electrical resistivity probe) geometry model definition.
    SmoothPipe:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Smooth pipe geometry model definition.
    WeldedJointUpstream:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        projectedAngleInDegrees:
          type: number
          description: 'Angle between the pipe axis and flow-facing surface of the weld [deg]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Welded joint (flow-facing side) geometry model definition.
    WeldedJointDownstream:
      type: object
      properties:
        geometryFactor:
          type: number
          description: 'Correction factor applied to results in order to account for isometric effects (swirl) [-]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        erosionAllowance:
          type: number
          description: 'Erosion allowance for component. Used for calculation of relative criticality [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        tag:
          type: string
          description: Component ID
          nullable: true
        material:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TargetMaterial'
        pipeDiameter:
          type: number
          description: 'Diameter of pipe [m]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
        weldHeight:
          type: number
          description: 'Height of weld as measured from the pipe wall [mm]'
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: Welded joint (downstream side) geometry model definition.
    ComponentsWrapper:
      type: object
      properties:
        bends:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bend'
          nullable: true
        tees:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tee'
          nullable: true
        reducers:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Reducer'
          nullable: true
        erProbes:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ErProbe'
          nullable: true
        smoothPipes:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/SmoothPipe'
          nullable: true
        weldedJointsUpstream:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/WeldedJointUpstream'
          nullable: true
        weldedJointsDownstream:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/WeldedJointDownstream'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
      description: "Contains definition of all components on the line. At least one of the arrays containing at least one component,\r\nhas to be specified."
    Line:
      type: object
      properties:
        tag:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        serviceLife:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        components:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentsWrapper'
      additionalProperties: false
      description: "Contains the Line definition, i.e. the virtual pipe containing a group of components for which erosion\r\nis to be calculated."
    LineBlackOilStream:
      type: object
      properties:
        fluidStream:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/BlackOilStream'
        particleStream:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ParticleStream'
        line:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Line'
